Package plugins

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExportArcAsciiGrid
    This tool can be used to export a Whitebox GAT raster file to an ArcGIS ASCII grid file.
    ExportArcGrid
    This tool can be used to export a Whitebox GAT raster file to an ArcGIS floating-point grid file.
    ExportGeoTiff
    This tool can be used to export a Whitebox GAT raster file to a GeoTIFF file (*.tif)
    ExportGML
    This tool can be used to export a vector shapefile file to an Geography Markup Language (GML) file.
    ExportGRASSAsciiGrid
    This tool can be used to export a Whitebox GAT raster file to a GRASS ASCII grid file.
    ExportIDRISIRaster
    This tool can be used to export Whitebox GAT raster files to IDRISI raster files (*.rdc and *.rst).
    ExportSagaGrid
    This tool can be used to export Whitebox GAT raster files to SAGA GIS raster files (*.sgrd and *.sdat).
    ExportSurferAsciiGrid
    This tool can be used to export a Whitebox GAT raster file to a Surfer (Golden Software) ASCII grid file.
    ExportWellKnownText
    This tool can be used to export a vector shapefile file to an Well-Known Text (WKT) file.
    ImportArcAsciiGrid
    This tool can be used to import an ArcGIS ASCII grid file to a Whitebox GAT raster file.
    ImportArcGrid
    This tool can be used to import an ArcGIS floating-point grid file into Whitebox GAT.
    ImportDEM
    This tool can be used to convert US Geological Survey/Canadian Digital Elevation Data (CDED) digital elevation models (DEMs) to Whitebox GAT raster files.
    ImportGenericMultibandData
    This tool can be used to import a number of generic multiband image data formats, including band interleaved by line (BIL), band interleaved by pixel (BIP), and band sequential (BSQ), to Whitebox GAT raster file format.
    ImportGeoTiff
    This tool can be used to import GeoTIFF files (*.tif) to Whitebox GAT raster files.
    ImportGRASSAsciiGrid
    This tool can be used to import a GRASS ASCII grid file to Whitebox GAT raster file format.
    ImportIDRISIRaster
    This tool can be used to import IDRISI raster files (*.rdc and *.rst) to Whitebox GAT raster files.
    ImportImage
    This tool can be used to import a number of common image formats to Whitebox GAT raster file format.
    ImportSagaGrid
    This tool can be used to convert SAGA GIS raster grids to Whitebox GAT raster files.
    ImportSRTM
    This tool can be used to convert Shuttle Radar Topography Mission (SRTM) digital elevation models (DEMs) to Whitebox GAT raster files.
    ImportSurferAsciiGrid
    This tool can be used to import a Surfer (Golden Software) ASCII grid file (*.grd) to a Whitebox GAT raster file.
    ImportTASVector
    This tool can be used to import vector files that were created using the Terrain Analysis System (TAS).
    ImportXYZToVectorPoints
    This tool can be used to import a series of x,y,z points into a vector shapefile of a POINT ShapeType.
